## WHAT IS REBALANCING ?
-------------------------

Rebalancing is the process in which Kafka redistributes the partitions of a topic among the consumers of a consumer group whenever the group membership changes,
such as when a new consumer joins or an existing consumer leaves or crashes. Rebalancing jab trigger hoti hai, us samay Partition Assignment Strategies ke
basis par ye decide kiya jata hai ki consumers ke beech partitions kaise redistribute honge. Hum already in Partition Assignment Strategies ko pehle hi padh chuke hain.

## PARTITION ASSIGNMENT STRATEGIES :
-------------------------------------

1. Range Assignor
2. Round Robin Assignor
3. Sticky Assignor
4. Cooperative Sticky Assignor


## EXAMPLE:
------------

Maan lo:

Topic = Orders

Aur Orders Topic ke paas 3 Partitions hain:

Orders
|
|-Partition-0
|-Partition-1
|-Partition-2

Maan lo 2 consumers (say Consumer-1 and Consumer-2) 'Orders' topic ko listen kar rahe hain aur dono same consumer group se belong karte hain, say 'order-group'.

order-group:
|
|- Consumer-1
|- Consumer-2


Is consumer-group ka Group Coordinator partition assignment kuch aisa kar sakta hai:

Partition-0 -> Consumer-1
Partition-1 -> Consumer-2
Partition-2 -> Consumer-1

Sab normal chal raha hai.

Rebalancing Kab Hota Hai?

Kafka ko jab pata chalta hai ki consumer group ki composition change ho gayi hai. 

---------------------------------
CASE 1: NAYA CONSUMER JOIN KARE
---------------------------------

Pehle:

Consumer-1
Consumer-2

Ab:

Consumer-1
Consumer-2
Consumer-3

Kafka sochega:

"Ab ek naya consumer aa gaya hai, kaam redistribute karna chahiye."

To reassignment karega using the configured Partition Assignment Strategy.

Example:

Partition-0 -> Consumer-1
Partition-1 -> Consumer-2
Partition-2 -> Consumer-3

Ye rebalancing hai.

---------------------------------
CASE 2: CONSUMER CRASH HO JAYE
---------------------------------

Pehle:

Partition-0 -> Consumer-1
Partition-1 -> Consumer-2
Partition-2 -> Consumer-1

Ab Consumer-2 crash ho gaya.

Kafka sochega:

"Partition-1 ko ab kaun consume karega?"

To reassignment karega using the configured Partition Assignment Strategy.

Example:

Partition-0 -> Consumer-1
Partition-1 -> Consumer-1
Partition-2 -> Consumer-1

Ye bhi rebalancing hai.

---------------------------------
CASE 3: CONSUMER RESTART HO
---------------------------------

Kafka ke liye restart bhi:

leave group
join group

jaisa hi hota hai.

Isliye rebalance trigger ho sakta hai.


