## WHY DO WE NEED CONSUMER GROUPS? WHY ARE STANDALONE CONSUMERS NOT ENOUGH?
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Standalone Consumers ke saath bhi hum topic ke different Partitions ko different Consumers
ko manually assign karke parallel processing achieve kar sakte hain.

To phir Consumer Groups ki zarurat kyu padi?

Consumer Groups parallel processing ke saath-saath bahut saare kaam automatically handle karte hain jo Standalone Consumers me hume manually manage karne padte hain.

Advantages of Consumer Groups:

1. Automatic Partition Assignment
   Kafka automatically decide karta hai ki kaunsi Partition kis Consumer ko milegi.

2. Automatic Rebalancing
   Agar koi Consumer crash ho jaye ya naya Consumer join kare,
   to Kafka automatically Partitions ko dubara assign kar deta hai.

3. Offset Management
   Kafka Consumer Group ke committed offsets ko track karta hai,


-------------
## IMPORTANT
-------------

Agar Standalone Consumers kisi Topic ko consume kar rahe hain,
to har Standalone Consumer ko us Topic ka complete data milega.


