- Agar Consumers Standalone hain, to Kafka koi Partition assignment nahi karta. Har Consumer khud manually decide karta hai ki use kaunsi Partition consume karni hai (using consumer.assign(...)).

Note:

Neeche diye gaye examples me hum Consumer Groups ko consider karenge.

