Partition-0
|
Offset 0:
|   |- Key   = User1
|   |- Value = Delhi
|
|
Offset 1:
|   |- Key   = User1
|   |- Value = Mumbai
|
Offset 2:
    |- Key   = User1
    |- Value = Bangalore



## KAFKA KYA DEKHEGA?

Kafka observe karega: 

Key = User1

multiple baar aa rahi hai.

To Kafka latest record preserve karega.


## AFTER COMPACTION :

Partition-0
|
Offset 2:
    |- Key   = User1
    |- Value = Bangalore


Delhi aur Mumbai wale purane records eventually remove ho gaye.


