## COMPACTION + RETENTION TOGETHER
-------------------------------------

Kafka me hum Retention aur Compaction dono ek saath use kar sakte hain.

## RETENTION & COMPACTION ENABLE KARTE HAIN:
-----------------------------------------------

##EXAMPLE:

@Bean
public NewTopic userProfileTopic() {
   return TopicBuilder.name("user-profile")
        .partitions(3)
        .replicas(3)
        .config(
           TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_CONFIG,
           TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_COMPACT + "," + TopicConfig.CLEANUP_POLICY_DELETE
         )
        .config(
           TopicConfig.RETENTION_MS_CONFIG,
           String.valueOf(30L * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000) // 30 Days
         )
        .build();
}


Meaning:

##1. COMPACTION

   Same KEY ke multiple records hain:

   (User1, Delhi)
   (User1, Mumbai)
   (User1, Bangalore)

   To Kafka eventually latest value preserve karega:

   (User1, Bangalore)

   Purane records corresponding to the same KEY
   eventually remove kiye ja sakte hain.


##2. RETENTION

   Agar data retention policy violate karta hai
   (for example 30 days se purana ho jata hai),
   to Kafka segment level cleanup perform kar sakta hai.


