1: IDEMPOTENT PRODUCER :
------------------------

Consider the previous example where Consumer-1 publishes events to payments topic.

In this scenario, Consumer-1 is acting as a Producer because it is producing messages to payments topic.

## PROBLEM
-------------

Maan lo Producer (Consumer-1) ek message publish karta hai:

Payment-101

payments topic me.

