Current State:

payments
  |
  partition-0 
    |
    |- Offset 0 -> Payment-101


Lekin Leader Replica dwara bheja gaya ACK network issue ki wajah se Producer (Consumer-1) tak pahunch nahi pata.

Manlo:

retries > 0

configured hai,

isliye Producer (Consumer-1) same message ko dobara publish (retry) karta hai.

