## OBSERVATION
----------------

Yahan:

✖ Consumer Crash nahi hua

✖ Offset Commit ka bhi koi issue nahi tha

Problem sirf Producer Retry ki wajah se hui.

Producer ko ACK nahi mila, isliye usne same message dobara bhej diya.

Aur Broker ne usse ek naya message samajh kar phir se store kar liya.


## RESULT:
-----------
payments topic me duplicate event create ho gaya.


## SOLUTION: USING AN IDEMPOTENT PRODUCER
-------------------------------------------

Agar Producer ko Leader Replica se ACK receive nahi hota (due to network issues, timeout, etc.), to Producer same message ko retry kar sakta hai.

Without idempotence, ye retries Kafka Topic me duplicate messages create kar sakti hain.

Isi Producer Retry wale duplicate message problem ko solve karne ke liye Kafka **Idempotent Producer** provide karta hai.

✔ Idempotent Producer ensure karta hai ki Producer retries ki wajah se same message Kafka topic ke Leader Replica par multiple baar store na ho.

Ye Producer ID (PID) aur Sequence Numbers ka use karke duplicate messages ko detect aur prevent karta hai.


## HOW IS AN IDEMPOTENT PRODUCER IMPLEMENTED?
----------------------------------------------

## QUESTION:

Leader Replica ko kaise pata chalega ki:

Payment-101

ek completely naya message hai

ya

Producer Retry ki wajah se dobara bheja gaya wahi message hai?

Kafka message content compare nahi karta, kyunki wo inefficient aur expensive hota hai.

Is problem ko solve karne ke liye Kafka internally do cheezein use karta hai:

1. Producer ID (PID)
2. Sequence Number


1. PRODUCER ID (PID)
---------------------

Jab Producer Idempotency enable karta hai:

enable.idempotence=true

to Kafka us Producer ko ek unique Producer ID (PID) assign karta hai.

Example:

Producer ID = 5001

Ab us Partition ke Leader Replica ko pata hota hai ki ye saare messages Producer-5001 se aa rahe hain.


2. SEQUENCE NUMBER
-------------------

Producer har message ke saath ek Sequence Number bhi send karta hai. 
Ye Sequence Number, Producer ID (PID) ke saath milkar us Producer dwara bheje gaye har message ko uniquely identify karta hai.

## EXAMPLE:
-------------

Producer ID = 5001

First Message
|
|- Payment-101
|- PID = 5001
|- Sequence = 0


Second Message
|
|- Payment-102
|- PID = 5001
|- Sequence = 1


Third Message
|
|- Payment-103
|- PID = 5001
|- Sequence = 2


## ACK SUCCESS SCENARIO
------------------------

Producer send karta hai:

Payment-101
PID = 5001
Sequence = 0

Broker message receive karta hai aur usse respective leader replica me successfully store kar deta hai.

## CURRENT STATE:

payments
|
Partition-0
 |
 Offset 0 -> Payment-101


Saath hi Leader Replica internally is Producer ke liye last successfully accepted Sequence Number maintain karti hai:

Producer ID = 5001
Last Sequence Number = 0


## ACK LOST SCENARIO
---------------------

Producer send karta hai:

Payment-101
PID = 5001
Sequence = 0

Broker message receive karta hai aur usse respective leader replica me successfully store kar deta hai.

## CURRENT STATE:

payments
|
Partition-0
 |
 Offset 0 -> Payment-101

Lekin network issue ki wajah se ACK Producer tak nahi pahunch pata.

Producer assume karta hai:

"Message publish fail ho gaya."

Agar retries > 0 configured hain, to Producer wahi message dobara send karta hai.


## IMPORTANT
-------------

Retry ke time Producer:

✔ Same Producer ID (PID)

✔ Same Sequence Number

send karta hai.

Retry Request:

Payment-101
PID = 5001
Sequence = 0


## BROKER DUPLICATE DETECTION
------------------------------

Leader Replica retry request receive karti hai.

Leader Replica check karti hai:

Producer ID = 5001
Sequence Number = 0

Leader Replica ke paas already record hota hai:

Producer ID = 5001
Last Sequence Number = 0

Isliye Leader Replica samajh jaati hai ki ye koi naya message nahi hai, balki pehle wale message ka retry hai.

Result:

Store Again ❌

Ignore Retry ✔

ACK Send ✔


## FINAL RESULT
----------------

payments 
|
Offset 0 -> Payment-101

Topic me sirf ek hi record store hoga.

Producer ne retry kiya, lekin Leader Replica ne Producer ID (PID) aur Sequence Number ki help se duplicate detect karke message ko dobara store nahi kiya.

Isi mechanism ki wajah se Idempotent Producer Producer Retries ki wajah se hone wale duplicate messages ko prevent karta hai.


